Author: Bhfad
Text: I'm guilty of this too, so don't feel like you're alone. Whenever I've gained a pound, I find myself thinking things like, "well that's what, 3.6k calories? I've already eaten a few thousand this month sooo.."

Author: redcapris
Text: There’s any episode of the kids show arthur where arthur eats way too much food and has a bunch of nightmares about it.... so relatable. Anyways there’s a part at the end where he sees a monster made out of all the food he’s ever eaten. And I think about that all the time!
